peace talks with other warring factions in the country.
</P>
<P>
In an exclusive interview at the Dar es Salaam International
Airport today, Buyoya also admitted that ethnic killings were
still going on in Burundi.
</P>
<P>
Muyoya, who was in Tanzania for a one-day working trip at the
