National Assembly, made a vehement objection against what is
written on Iraq in the final communique of the 7th Conference of
the Arab Parliamentary Union (APU).
</P>
<P>
Hammadi, who leads his country's delegation to the conference,
rejected the implied accusation that Iraq has not fully fulfilled
its commitment to the U.N. resolutions on Kuwait.
</P>
