according to resolution 833 and has sent back all Kuwaiti
property and paid the necessary compensations besides returning
the Kuwaiti and other nationalities' captives," he said.
</P>
<P>
Iraq is further cooperating with the Red Cross on the fate of
the missing, the Iraqi speaker added, clarifying that by doing all
this, Iraq has already honored all the international resolutions
on it.
</P>
<P>
Leading Arab lawmakers, winding up their two-day meeting here
today, while advocating the unity of Iraq, stressed that Iraq
should implement all U.N. Security Council resolutions so as to
expedite the lifting of the embargo imposed on it for its 1990
invasion of Kuwait.
</P>
<P>
Iraq has been urging Arab countries to give a helping hand in
lifting the U.N.-imposed six-year sanctions as early as this
year. 
