<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 15 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major world
cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on May 16, issued by China's
Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 15 degrees c., max. 26 degrees c., clear, fresh
to strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 16 degrees c., max. 21 degrees c., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
