</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 9 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 12 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 10 degrees c., max. 18 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 8 degrees c., max. 19 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
