<HEADLINE> Chinese, French Presidents Hold Talks (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jiang expressed his appreciation for Chirac's efforts to
highly value Sino-French relations, make a wise decision on the
issues of arms sales to Taiwan and human rights, and advocate
and actively promote the establishment of a comprehensive
partnership between the two countries.
</P>
