common concern with leaders and personages from various circles of
these countries to increase understanding and expand co-operation,
Shen said.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman expressed his convinction that Li's visit will be
conducive not only to the promotion of exchanges and cooperation
between the CPPCC National Committee and the governments and
parliaments of the three countries but to the advancement of the
friendly and cooperative ties between China and three countries
and the rest of Western Europe.
</P>
<P>
Li will be the guest of President Almeida Santos of the
Assembly of the Republic of Portugal, President Apostolos
Kaklamanis of the Parliament of the Hellenic Republic, and the
Government of the Federal Republic of Germany. 
