<HEADLINE> Philippine Offers a Bridge to Panama </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PANAMA CITY, May 14 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Philippine President
Fidel Ramos pledged today to boost economic ties with Panama and
said his country is willing to serve as a bridge to Asian
economies for Panama.
</P>
<P>
This was a time for Panama and the Philippines to develop
economic ties, Ramos said. He added that he wanted to invite
Panamanians to look to the Philippines as their gateway to Asia
and the Pacific.
